snippet.title: Takoway Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Takoway is a perspective-based puzzle game that is hard on the outside but squishy on the inside. Follow Tako the hexapus as she goes on a six-legged journey to find belonging away from captivity.

Coming to Apple's App Store and Android's Play Store on 3rd October 2019.
Pre-Order now on Apple App Store: http://bit.ly/TakowayiOS
Pre-Register now on Android Play Store: http://bit.ly/TakowayAndroid
